[I] Open source RDP server

[T] xrdp provides a graphical login to remote machines using RDP (Microsoft
[T] Remote Desktop Protocol). xrdp accepts connections from variety of RDP
[T] clients.

[U] https://www.xrdp.org/

[A] Xrdp Authors
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/x11

[L] APL
